UTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"server_error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Several Pods of the frontend service show a significant increase in `rrt_max`, `rrt`, `server_error_ratio`, and `error_ratio` during the fault period, indicating performance issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend pods `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, and `frontend-2` experienced a notable increase in response time and server error ratios with `rrt_max` nearing 60000000 from normal medians around 200000-300000 and server error ratios rising to around 0.3.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"The `checkoutservice-2` pod shows an unusual increase in `pod_cpu_usage`, potentially linking to performance drops.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"The `pod_cpu_usage` increased from 0.01 to 0.2 during the fault period, with a `median_change_ratio` of 1.8095.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"The `redis-cart-0` pod shows a slight increase in `pod_cpu_usage`, although less significant compared to other metrics.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"This pod experienced a `pod_cpu_usage` change from 0.04 to 0.13 with a `p99_change_ratio` of 1.0481.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"The `cartservice-0` pod showed increased `client_error_ratio` and `error_ratio` indicating possible reliability issues during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Both `client_error_ratio` and `error_ratio` metrics showed p99 values peaking around 21.71 from a normal of 0. Additionally, `rrt_max` increased from a median of 6307.5 to 1040.0.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些异常说明在故障期间，多个服务和 pod 的性能指标显著变差，尤其是 `frontend` 服务和 `checkoutservice-2`, `redis-cart-0`, `cartservice-0` pods。这些问题可能需要进一步排查应用层代码或架构配置。"}
